图模型
Neo4j 存的是关系网络，不是全量业务数据——规则卡关联链路、菜品相似度、门店经验迁移路径：

节点:
  Store {id, name, brand}
  DishRef {saas_item_id, name}          — SaaS 菜品引用（不落主数据，只存引用）
  ComboRef {saas_combo_key, name}       — SaaS 套餐引用
  RuleCard {rule_no, content, risk_type, store_id}
  CaseCard {case_no, action, result, store_id}
  Redline {redline_no, content, store_ids}
  CustomerSegment {age, scene, preference}
  SceneTag {name}

关系:
  (Store)-[:HAS_RULE]->(RuleCard)
  (Store)-[:HAS_CASE]->(CaseCard)
  (Redline)-[:APPLIES_TO]->(Store)
  (RuleCard)-[:REFERENCES]->(DishRef)
  (RuleCard)-[:TARGETS]->(CustomerSegment)
  (CaseCard)-[:DERIVED_FROM]->(RuleCard)
  (DishRef)-[:BELONGS_TO]->(ComboRef)
  (DishRef)-[:SIMILAR_TO {score}]->(DishRef)
  (Store)-[:SAME_BRAND]->(Store)
  (Store)-[:MIGRATES_TO {confidence}]->(Store)
典型 Cypher 查询
// 1. 查某门店适用的全部规则（门店专属 + 全局）
MATCH (s:Store {id: $store_id})-[:HAS_RULE]->(r:RuleCard)
WHERE r.status IN ['verified', 'unverified']
RETURN r.rule_no, r.content, r.risk_type
UNION
MATCH (r:RuleCard)
WHERE r.store_id IS NULL AND r.status IN ['verified', 'unverified']
RETURN r.rule_no, r.content, r.risk_type

// 2. 查某菜品的所有相似品（跨门店）
MATCH (d:DishRef {saas_item_id: $item_id})-[:SIMILAR_TO]->(s:DishRef)
RETURN s.name, s.saas_item_id

// 3. 查某案例关联的规则链
MATCH (c:CaseCard {case_no: 'C-001'})-[:DERIVED_FROM]->(r:RuleCard)
OPTIONAL MATCH (r)-[:TARGETS]->(cs:CustomerSegment)
RETURN c, r, cs

// 4. 门店间可迁移经验
MATCH (s1:Store {id: 's001'})-[:HAS_CASE]->(c:CaseCard {result_judgment: 'positive'})
MATCH (c)-[:DERIVED_FROM]->(r:RuleCard)-[:TARGETS]->(cs:CustomerSegment)
MATCH (s2:Store) WHERE s2.id <> 's001'
RETURN s2.name, c.reusable_conclusion, c.non_migration_boundary
